    <item>
      <title>Cathie Wood 欢迎 AI 竞争，因为 DeepSeek 可以降低成本</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/ark-s-wood-welcomes-ai-competition-as-deepseek-could-lower-costs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Ark Investment Management 首席执行官 Cathie Wood 表示，随着中国 DeepSeek 的出现，人工智能领域的竞争加剧是一个积极的发展，将有助于科技公司削减成本并改进平台。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/ark-s-wood-welcomes-ai-competition-as-deepseek-could-lower-costs</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 11:46:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
